(263, '177', '', '345', '566.0', '345', '4556', 'Document the main reason the patient came for consultation (chief complaint). Provide a detailed history of the present illness including onset, duration, progression, associated symptoms, and any treatments already taken. Include past medical or surgical history, family medical history, and social history such as smoking, alcohol intake, occupation, and lifestyle factors.\r\n', NULL, NULL, 'Based on the history and physical examination, provide the most likely clinical diagnosis. Include primary diagnosis and any secondary or differential diagnoses if applicable.', 'List any laboratory tests, imaging studies, or other investigations required to confirm diagnosis or guide treatment. Include both ordered and pending investigations where necessary.', 'List any laboratory tests, imaging studies, or other investigations required to confirm diagnosis or guide treatment. Include both ordered and pending investigations where necessary.', '', '2026-02-18', '2026-02-18 05:58:32', 'Perform and document findings from a systematic physical examination. Include general examination and specific system reviews such as head and neck, cardiovascular system, respiratory system, abdominal examination, musculoskeletal system, neurological assessment, and any other relevant findings.', 'umoh ekpo', NULL, NULL, NULL, 345, 10, 45.00, 67.00, 330.90, 564.00, '', '00:00:00', 'cough', NULL),
